  "action_title": "Reduce seabird bycatch by releasing offal overboard when setting longlines",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\nTwo replicated and controlled studies in the South Atlantic and sub-Antarctic Indian Ocean found significant reductions in the number of albatross and petrels attacking baits and being caught when offal was released overboard during line setting."
}

